description: Ralph Gleason's Jazz Casual TV Show (UK) featured numerous Jazz artist to include The Julian Cannonball Adderley Quintet. Although this episode is an abbreviated version it portrays the essence of both Host and Artist. The graphics and titling are mine so to ID the musicians, songs and composers as well as cover up previous graphics from a Public Access Show from which this footage came from. In keeping with professional courtesy I have to acknowledge Ralph Gleason and the Jazz Casual as well as "BOFFO!" for supplying this footage and The Julian Cannonball Adderley Quintet for the performance.
